# Operator's local study materials — never commit to the public repo.
# Drop test PDFs / reference HTML in the project root for local use; they
# stay out of git. (Future: move to fiszkomat/corpus/ if it makes sense
# to organise.)
*.pdf
fiszki-*.html
Leki-*.html

# Cards JSON sidecars from local generation — ignored by default,
# *except* the curated landing-page sample decks (whitelisted below).
test_docs/out/*.cards.json

# Curated sample decks shipped with the code so /study/sample/<slug>
# and the landing "FISZKI PRZYKŁADOWE" section work on a fresh checkout.
